snippet.title: Demonetisation: Can Use Old Rs 500 Note for Fuel, Air Ticket Purchase till Dec 2

localized.description:
Demonetisation: Last day to use your old Rs 500 note for fuel, air ticket purchase is December 2. Rs 1000 note already out of use.
